invariant io_extra72.BufferedReader_mro_4:
  description: "BufferedReader.__mro__.__len__() == 4 — the MRO for BufferedReader is [BufferedReader, BufferedIOBase, IOBase, object] with 4 entries; no prior io spec checks BufferedReader.__mro__.__len__() in iohier72 namespace; novel MRO length anchor; verified Python 3.14.3 macOS/Darwin 25.4.0"
